<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا تَرْكَنُوا}</span> ... لَا تَمِيلُوا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَرَفَيِ النَّهَارِ}</span> ... الصَّبَاحَ وَالمَسَاءَ،<span class="c5"> وقِيلَ:</span> المُرَادُ بِهَا: صَلَاةُ الفَجْرِ وَالظُّهْرِ وَالعَصْرِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَزُلَفًا مِّنَ اللَّيْلِ}</span> ... سَاعَاتٍ مِنَ اللَّيْلِ،<span class="c5"> وقِيلَ:</span> المُرَادُ بِهَا: المَغْرِبُ وَالعِشَاءُ، أَوِ العِشَاءُ وَحْدَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَوْلَا}</span> ... فَهَلَّا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْقُرُونِ}</span> ... الأُمَمِ المَاضِيَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُوْلُوا بَقِيَّةٍ}</span> ... بَقَايَا مِنْ أَهْلِ الخَيْرِ وَالصَّلَاحِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُتْرِفُوا فِيهِ}</span> ... مُتِّعُوا فِيهِ مِنْ لَذَّاتِ الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُمَّةً وَاحِدَةً}</span> ... جَمَاعَةً وَاحِدَةً عَلَى دِينٍ وَاحِدٍ، وَهُوَ الإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَكَانَتِكُمْ}</span> ... حَالَتِكُمْ، وَطَرِيقَتِكُمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>